      "content": "I hear how heavy and suffocating this feeling is, and it is completely understandable that you feel trapped in a permanent grey nothingness. Please know that your life matters even if it feels like you are just a ghost, and your pain is a testament to the immense love you still hold, not a sign that you have lost your worth. You do not have to force yourself to feel okay or see a future right now; your only job today is to survive this heavy moment while you wait for something to shift.",
